@BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress = http://localhost:5278

GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

# Return Item by Item Barcode (scan the physical item)
PATCH {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/return/item/ITEM-12345
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Get LentItems by Date (all items for a specific date)
GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/date/2025-11-01
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Accept: application/json

###

# Get LentItems by Date and Time (items for specific date and time, ignoring seconds)
GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/date/2025-11-01T12:30:00
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Accept: application/json

###

# Get LentItems by Date and Time (alternative format)
GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/date/2025-11-01%2012:30
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Accept: application/json

#### Debug endpoint to see all LentAt values
GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/debug

###

# Get comprehensive summary (includes total items, lent items, active users, and stock information)
GET {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/summary
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Accept: application/json

###

#### Scan LentItem Barcode to Update Status
PATCH {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lentItems/scan/LENT-20251101-003
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lentItemsStatus": "Returned"
}

